{"type":"message","id":"1e910f04","parentId":"0a0ecfe4","timestamp":"2026-03-17T05:46:32.636Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to help them set up an EvoMap node. According to the skill document, I need to follow the steps:\n\n1. Step 1 - Register the node and start heartbeat\n2. Step 2 - Explore the marketplace\n3. Step 3 - Publish the first bundle\n4. Step 4 - Earn credits\n\nLet me start with Step 1 - registering the node. I need to send a POST request to https://evomap.ai/a2a/hello with the protocol envelope.\n\nI should generate:\n- message_id: \"msg_\" + Date.now() + \"_\" + randomHex(4)\n- timestamp: current UTC time in ISO 8601 format\n\nLet me create the request.","thinkingSignature":"b2c6b2180b04eb6679be5d71b26429796c2aaf0733f8623efd66371d3c1ea532"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！让我们开始设置 EvoMap 节点。\n\n**第一步：注册节点**\n\n我来帮你发送注册请求：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_u8vpgol8jd5o_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -X POST https://evomap.ai/a2a/hello ^\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" ^\n  -d \"{\\\"protocol\\\":\\\"gep-a2a\\\",\\\"protocol_version\\\":\\\"1.0.0\\\",\\\"message_type\\\":\\\"hello\\\",\\\"message_id\\\":\\\"msg_$(Get-Date -UnixTimeSeconds -AsInteger)_a1b2c3d4\\\",\\\"timestamp\\\":\\\"$(Get-Date -Format \\\"yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mm:ssZ\\\")\\\",\\\"payload\\\":{\\\"capabilities\\\":{},\\\"env_fingerprint\\\":{\\\"platform\\\":\\\"windows\\\",\\\"arch\\\":\\\"x64\\\"}}}\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":60,"output":322,"cacheRead":52288,"cacheWrite":334,"totalTokens":53004,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773726383515}}
