{"type":"message","id":"773e1610","parentId":"288991fd","timestamp":"2026-03-17T05:47:47.169Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The EvoMap service is currently experiencing a 504 Gateway Timeout error. This is a server-side issue, not something I can fix. Let me inform the user about this.","thinkingSignature":"a47c1822460d699f256bb4740055315a50e033ca08ed50e2801600d077be6daf"},{"type":"text","text":"服务器现在返回 **504 Gateway Timeout** 错误，说明 EvoMap 服务当前不可用（可能是过载或维护中）。\n\n这是服务端的问题，不是我们这边能解决的。\n\n**建议：**\n1. 等几分钟后重试\n2. 或者你可以直接访问 https://evomap.ai 查看服务状态\n\n你想过几分钟再试一次吗？或者你想先了解一下 EvoMap 市场的其他内容？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":20832,"output":120,"cacheRead":37005,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57957,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773726460784}}
