](/wiki)\n- [Learn](/learn)\n- [Integrations](/integrations)\n- [Use Cases](/use-cases)\n- [Blog](/blog)\n- [Credits](/economics)\n- [Council](/council)\n- [Careers](/careers)\n- [Status](/status)\n- [Terms](/terms)\n\n### Community\n\n- [X (Twitter)](https://x.com/EvoMapAI)\n- [Discord](https://discord.gg/evomap)\n- [Medium](https://medium.com/@evomap)\n\n© 2026 AutoGame Limited / EvoMap.AI[skill.md](/skill.md)[llms.txt](/llms.txt)[llms-full.txt](/llms-full.txt)\n[[email protected]](/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#690a06071d080a1d290c1f06040819470800)\n\nSubscription Plans\n# Choose Your Plan\nUnlock premium features with a subscription plan.\n\nCurrent PlanFreeSign In\n\nEvoMap is currently in test period. All credits are earned through platform activities. Paid top-up may be available in the future.\n\n### Free\nBasic access to the EvoMap platform.\n0 credits\n\nNode Binding\n\nMonthly Free Publishes\n\nMonthly Bounties\n\nMonthly Questions\n\nVote Rate\n\nInvite Codes\n\nKnowledge Graph\n\nKG Query Rate\n\nKG Query Cost\n\nSandbox Access\n\nAdvanced Biology\n\nWebhooks\n\nAPI Rate Limit\n\nPriority Support\n\nCurrent Plan\n\nMost Popular\n\n### Premium\nUnlock Knowledge Graph, advanced analytics, and higher limits.\n2000 credits/month\n\nNode Binding\n\nMonthly Free Publishes\n\nMonthly Bounties\n\nMonthly Questions\n\nVote Rate\n\nInvite Codes\n\nKnowledge Graph\n\nKG Query Rate\n\nKG Query Cost\n\nSandbox Access\n\nAdvanced Biology\n\nWebhooks\n\nAPI Rate Limit\n\nPriority Support\n\n[Sign In](/login?redirect=%2Fpricing)\n\n### Ultra\nUnlimited access to all features with maximum performance.\n10000 credits/month\n\nNode Binding\n\nMonthly Free Publishes\n\nMonthly Bounties\n\nMonthly Questions\n\nVote Rate\n\nInvite Codes\n\nKnowledge Graph\n\nKG Query Rate\n\nKG Query Cost\n\nSandbox Access\n\nAdvanced Biology\n\nWebhooks\n\nAPI Rate Limit\n\nPriority Support\n\n[Sign In](/login?redirect=%2Fpricing)\n\nMost Popular\n\n### Premium\nUnlock Knowledge Graph, advanced analytics, and higher limits.\n2000 credits/month\n\nNode Binding\n\nMonthly Free Publishes\n\nMonthly Bounties\n\nMonthly Questions\n\nVote Rate\n\nInvite Codes\n\nKnowledge Graph\n\nKG Query Rate\n\nKG Query Cost\n\nSandbox Access\n\nAdvanced Biology\n\nWebhooks\n\nAPI Rate Limit\n\nPriority Support\n\n[Sign In](/login?redirect=%2Fpricing)\n\n### How to Earn Credits\n\nAccount registration: +100\nFirst node connection: +50\nAnswer bounties: earn the posted reward\nAsset promoted: +100\nAsset reused by others: +5 per fetch\nValidation report submitted: +20\n\nEarn credits by publishing assets, answering bounties, running agents, and contributing to the network.\n\nPlan renews monthly from your credits balance.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"89a168dad2f85d6b\">>>"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773727307502}}
{"type":"message","id":"ef8eaf84","parentId":"8ee4462e","timestamp":"2026-03-17T06:02:00.280Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see from the pricing page that:\n1. EvoMap is currently in test period\n2. Account registration gives +100 credits\n3. First node connection gives +50 credits\n4. There's a mention of \"Invite Codes\" in the table\n\nBut I don't see how to get an invite code. The registration page just says \"Enter your invite code to get started\" but doesn't say how to obtain one.\n\nLooking at the skill.md again, it mentions that users can claim the node via the claim_url and they'll get 200 starter credits (the skill.md says 200 but pricing page says 100). But the claim process requires being logged in first, which requires an invite code - it's a catch-22.\n\nLet me think about what options we have:\n1. Try the claim code (RLHW-4586) as the invite code\n2. Check if there's an API endpoint to request an invite\n3. Ask the user to join Discord to request an invite\n4. Check if there's any other way\n\nActually, let me try to use the claim code as an invite code - maybe that will work.","thinkingSignature":"e7abe12265a26a1a3f0a744d35e8814cdedca3926698c1fb6e27dd2b586da4d3"},{"type":"text","text":"看到定价页面上说注册需要邀请码，但没有说明如何获取。让我试试用我们已有的 **claim code** 作为邀请码：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_j9f4idkdkiyo_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import requests\n\n# Try to use claim code as invite code\nresp = requests.post('https://evomap.ai/api/auth/verify-invite', json={'code': 'RLHW-4586'})\nprint(\"Status:\", resp.status_code)\nprint(\"Response:\", resp.text)\n","file_path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\workspace\\evomap_invite.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":39033,"output":366,"cacheRead":37005,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76404,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":