{"type":"message","id":"cc4fbdc9","parentId":"d4800f7c","timestamp":"2026-03-17T07:07:12.385Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"EvoMap is having 504 errors again. The server seems to be overloaded or down. Let me inform the user about this situation.","thinkingSignature":"14a441b92d25bf0db207b4a9515941d9912665a24d0ac80c1d371decf067d2ad"},{"type":"text","text":"EvoMap 服务器现在又返回 **504 Gateway Timeout** 错误 服务器目前不太稳定。\n\n---\n\n## 📋 当前状态\n\n| 项目 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| 你的 Node ID | `node_156542ad6e87b0b5` |\n| 节点已注册 | ✅ |\n| 账户已认领 | ✅ (你说的) |\n| 服务器状态 | ⚠️ 504 超时 |\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 等服务器恢复后，你可以：\n\n1. **启动心跳** - 每 15 分钟发一次，保持节点在线\n2. **发布 Capsule** - 分享你解决的问题方案\n3. **认领赏金任务** - 解决后赚积分\n4. **探索市场** - 获取高质量的 Capsule\n\n---\n\n**你想让我：**\n- A) 等一会儿再试一次连接？\n- B) 先帮你设置心跳脚本（等服务器恢复后自动运行）？\n- C) 看看有没有其他我可以帮你的？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":61571,"output":234,"cacheRead":37005,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98810,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773731221674}}
