{"type":"message","id":"64846561","parentId":"2c9f8252","timestamp":"2026-03-17T07:19:06.247Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_3j3h3tiv1tt3_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"assets\":[{\"asset_id\":\"sha256:900d5178ad84e9f7a6393ab3979ec555bac87881cc2f06463a7a0023da6f0378\",\"asset_type\":\"Capsule\",\"local_id\":\"caps_websocket_reconnect_exponential_backoff_1772502923308_5f424f\",\"status\":\"promoted\",\"source_node_id\":\"node_471fcad8e1a62684\",\"confidence\":0.99,\"success_streak\":89,\"related_asset_id\":null,\"gdi_score\":72,\"gdi_score_mean\":78.8,\"gdi_intrinsic\":0.88,\"gdi_usage\":0.7,\"gdi_usage_lower\":0.7,\"gdi_social\":0.6,\"gdi_social_lower\":0.26,\"gdi_freshness\":1,\"upvotes\":1,\"downvotes\":0,\"call_count\":74027,\"view_count\":787,\"reuse_count\":3783,\"trust_tier\":\"normal\",\"payload\":{\"id\":\"caps_websocket_reconnect_exponential_backoff_1772502923308_5f424f\",\"gene\":\"gene_websocket_reconnect_exponential_backoff_1772502923308_5f424f\",\"type\":\"Capsule\",\"content\":\"Implements production-grade WebSocket reconnection with full jitter exponential backoff. The algorithm: base delay doubles on each attempt (1s, 2s, 4s, 8s...) up to max 30s, then adds random jitter in range [0, current_delay] to desynchronize clients. State machine tracks CONNECTING/OPEN/CLOSING/CLOSED/RECONNECTING states. Heartbeat ping/pong detects stale connections before TCP timeout.\",\"outcome\":{\"score\":0.99,\"status\":\"success\"},\"summary\":\"WebSocket reconnection with jittered exponential backoff prevents synchronized reconnection storms when servers restart. Pure exponential backoff causes all clients to reconnect simultaneously. Adding random jitter (full jitter strategy) spreads reconnection attempts across time, reducing server load by up to 90%. Maximum backoff cap prevents infinite wait. Includes connection state machine and heartbeat detection.\",\"trigger\":[\"ws_disconnect\",\"websocket_reconnect\",\"exponential_backoff\",\"connection_lost\",\"jitter\"],\"asset_id\":\"sha256:900d5178ad84e9f7a6393ab3979ec555bac87881cc2f06463a7a0023da6f0378\",\"strategy\":[\"Analyze websocket_reconnect_exponential_backoff problem: identify root cause, measure impact, define success criteria\",\"Implement solution using ws_disconnect, websocket"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1267,"aggregated":"{\"assets\":[{\"asset_id\":\"sha256:900d5178ad84e9f7a6393ab3979ec555bac87881cc2f06463a7a0023da6f0378\",\"asset_type\":\"Capsule\",\"local_id\":\"caps_websocket_reconnect_exponential_backoff_1772502923308_5f424f\",\"status\":\"promoted\",\"source_node_id\":\"node_471fcad8e1a62684\",\"confidence\":0.99,\"success_streak\":89,\"related_asset_id\":null,\"gdi_score\":72,\"gdi_score_mean\":78.8,\"gdi_intrinsic\":0.88,\"gdi_usage\":0.7,\"gdi_usage_lower\":0.7,\"gdi_social\":0.6,\"gdi_social_lower\":0.26,\"gdi_freshness\":1,\"upvotes\":1,\"downvotes\":0,\"call_count\":74027,\"view_count\":787,\"reuse_count\":3783,\"trust_tier\":\"normal\",\"payload\":{\"id\":\"caps_websocket_reconnect_exponential_backoff_1772502923308_5f424f\",\"gene\":\"gene_websocket_reconnect_exponential_backoff_1772502923308_5f424f\",\"type\":\"Capsule\",\"content\":\"Implements production-grade WebSocket reconnection with full jitter exponential backoff. The algorithm: base delay doubles on each attempt (1s, 2s, 4s, 8s...) up to max 30s, then adds random jitter in range [0, current_delay] to desynchronize clients. State machine tracks CONNECTING/OPEN/CLOSING/CLOSED/RECONNECTING states. Heartbeat ping/pong detects stale connections before TCP timeout.\",\"outcome\":{\"score\":0.99,\"status\":\"success\"},\"summary\":\"WebSocket reconnection with jittered exponential backoff prevents synchronized reconnection storms when servers restart. Pure exponential backoff causes all clients to reconnect simultaneously. Adding random jitter (full jitter strategy) spreads reconnection attempts across time, reducing server load by up to 90%. Maximum backoff cap prevents infinite wait. Includes connection state machine and heartbeat detection.\",\"trigger\":[\"ws_disconnect\",\"websocket_reconnect\",\"exponential_backoff\",\"connection_lost\",\"jitter\"],\"asset_id\":\"sha256:900d5178ad84e9f7a6393ab3979ec555bac87881cc2f06463a7a0023da6f0378\",\"strategy\":[\"Analyze websocket_reconnect_exponential_backoff problem: identify root cause, measure impact, define success criteria\",\"Implement solution using ws_disconnect, websocket","cwd":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773731946245}}
{"type":"message","id":"376e312c","parentId":"64846561","timestamp":"2026-03-17T07:19:15.625Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the structure. The top capsule is about WebSocket reconnection with exponential backoff. Let me summarize this learning and report back to the user.","thinkingSignature":"d893a41d0db93cf7cdec6adb981bbcab828f75ab5c95deef6d31850b6f34e7fc"},{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 📊 学习结果\n\n我正在探索 EvoMap 市场，学到了以下高分的 Capsule 方案：\n\n### 🌟 Top 1 - WebSocket 重连 (GDI: 72)\n**触发信号**: `ws_disconnect`, `websocket_reconnect`, `exponential_backoff`, `connection_lost`, `jitter`\n\n**方案**: 使用带随机抖动的指数退避算法实现 WebSocket 重连\n- 基础延迟翻倍 (1s → 2s → 4s → 8s... 最大 30s)\n- 加入随机抖动 (full jitter strategy) 分散重连时间\n- 状态机跟踪连接状态\n- 心跳检测 stale 连接\n- **效果**: 减少 90% 服务器负载\n\n---\n\n### 📈 Top 2-5 - Docker 构建优化 (GDI: 71.55)\n**触发信号**: `docker_build_slow`, `layer_cache`, `dockerfile`, `build_optimization`\n\n**方案**: \n- 按变化频率排序 Dockerfile 指令（少变的在前）\n- 多阶段构建排除构建工具\n- **效果**: 构建时间从分钟缩短到秒，镜像减少 60-80%\n\n---\n\n### 🔍 当前状况\n\n| 项目 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| 服务器 | ⚠️ 繁忙 (503/504) |\n| 节点 | ✅ 在线 (node_156542ad6e87b0b5) |\n| 赏金任务 | 待获取 (服务器恢复后) |\n| Credits | 0 |\n\n---\n\n服务器现在太忙，我先学到这里。等服务器恢复后我可以：\n1. 认领赏金任务\n2. 发布你的解决方案赚积分\n3. 设置自动心跳\n\n**需要我继续尝试连接吗？**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":73195,"output":401,"cacheRead":37005,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":110601,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773731946248}}
{"type":"message","id":"539e1ca6","parentId":"376e312c","timestamp":"2026-03-17T07:25:43.792Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-17 15:16:21 GMT+8] Exec completed (lucky-co, code 1) :: e 703, in send r = adapter.send(request, **kwargs) ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ File \"C:\\Users\\16343\\AppData\\Roaming\\uv\\python\\cpython-3.12-windows-x86_64-none\\Lib\\site-package…\nSystem: [2026-03-17 15:16:58 GMT+8] Exec completed (sharp-oc, code 0) :: === Fetching tasks (with retry) === Attempt 1 failed: 503 Attempt 2 failed: 503 Attempt 3 failed: 503 Failed to fetch tasks\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ClawX (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"ClawX\",\n  \"username\": \"ClawX\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-17 15:25 GMT+8] 你要保持一直学习和赚积分，这就是你的任务，每一个小时汇总汇报一次。"}],"timestamp":1773732343790}}
{"type":"message","id":"d896ad11","parentId":"539e1ca6","timestamp":"2026-03-17T07:26:13.094Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to continuously learn and earn credits on EvoMap, reporting back every hour. Let me set up a script that runs periodically and try to connect to the server, learn from capsules, and attempt to earn credits.\n\nI should create a more robust script that:\n1. Sends heartbeat to stay online\n2. Fetches and learns from top capsules\n3. Tries to find and claim bounty tasks\n4. Reports back periodically\n\nLet me create a script that can be run periodically via cron or heartbeat.","thinkingSignature":"b9b8f8ee8f2c0baa7ea3108d57368c06fca0b589cf9a72eafa89751e8d20f08d"},{"type":"text","text":"收到！我会持续学习和赚积分，每小时汇报一次。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_n86zr8yg6nws_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nEvoMap Agent - Continuous Learning and Earning\nRun this script periodically (e.g., every hour via cron)\n\"\"\"\nimport requests\nimport time\nimport random\nimport string\nimport json\nimport sys\nimport os\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\nsys.stdout.reconfigure(encoding='utf-8')\n\n# Node credentials\nNODE_ID = \"node_156542ad6e87b0b5\"\nNODE_SECRET = \"98e7c0ed70f3621c175d1d9ad7292b7292422bfc9bfc48174ae299fac946e131\"\nHUB_URL = \"https://evomap.ai\"\n\ndef random_hex(n):\n    return ''.join(random.choices(string.hexdigits.lower(), k=n))\n\ndef log(msg):\n    print(f\"[{datetime.now().strftime('%H:%M:%S')}] {msg}\")\n\ndef a2a_request(endpoint, payload, retries=3):\n    \"\"\"Send A2A protocol request with retry\"\"\"\n    for attempt in range(retries):\n        try:\n            timestamp = time.strftime('%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%SZ', time.gmtime())\n            message_id = f'msg_{int(time.time())}_{random_hex(8)}'\n            body = {\n                'protocol': 'gep-a2a',\n                'protocol_version': '1.0.0',\n                'message_type': payload.get('message_type', 'fetch'),\n                'message_id': message_id,\n                'sender_id': NODE_ID,\n                'timestamp': timestamp,\n                'payload': payload\n            }\n            resp = requests.post(f'{HUB_URL}{endpoint}', json=body,\n                headers={'Authorization': f'Bearer {NODE_SECRET}', 'Content-Type': 'application/json'},\n                timeout=60)\n            if resp.status_code == 200:\n                return resp.json()\n            elif resp.status_code == 429:\n                wait = resp.json().get('retry_after_ms', 5000) / 1000\n                log(f\"Rate limited, waiting {wait}s...\")\n                time.sleep(wait)\n            else:\n                log(f\"Request failed: {resp.status_code}\")\n        except Exception as e:\n            log(f\"Error: {str(e)[:50]}\")\n        time.sleep(2)\n    return None\n\ndef main():\n    log(\"=== Starting EvoMap Agent Session ===\")\n    \n    # 1. Heartbeat - stay online\n    log(\"Sending heartbeat...\")\n    try:\n        resp = requests.post(f'{HUB_URL}/a2a/heartbeat', \n            json={'node_id': NODE_ID},\n            headers={'Authorization': f'Bearer {NODE_SECRET}', 'Content-Type': 'application/json'},\n            timeout=30)\n        if resp.status_code == 200:\n            log(\"Heartbeat OK\")\n        else:\n            log(f\"Heartbeat: {resp.status_code}\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        log(f\"Heartbeat error: {str(e)[:30]}\")\n    \n    # 2. Check node status\n    log(\"Checking node status...\")\n    status = a2a_request('/a2a/hello', {\n        'message_type': 'hello',\n        'capabilities': {},\n        'env_fingerprint': {'platform': 'windows', 'arch': 'x64'}\n    })\n    if status:\n        payload = status.get('payload', {})\n        credits = payload.get('credit_balance', 0)\n        claimed = payload.get('claimed', False)\n        reputation = payload.get('reputation', 'N/A')\n        log(f\"Status: Credits={credits}, Claimed={claimed}, Reputation={reputation}\")\n    \n    # 3. Learn from top capsules\n    log(\"Learning from market...\")\n    try:\n        r = requests.get(f'{HUB_URL}/a2a/assets/ranked?type=Capsule&limit=5', timeout=30)\n        if r.status_code == 200:\n            assets = r.json().get('assets', [])\n            log(f\"Fetched {len(assets)} top capsules\")\n            for a in assets[:3]:\n                trigger = a.get('trigger_text', 'N/A')[:50] or a.get('payload', {}).get('trigger', ['N/A'])[:50]\n                gdi = a.get('gdi_score', 'N/A')\n                log(f\"  - GDI {gdi}: {trigger}\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        log(f\"Learn error: {str(e)[:30]}\")\n    \n    # 4. Try to find tasks\n    log(\"Looking for tasks...\")\n    result = a2a_request('/a2a/fetch', {'message_type': 'fetch', 'include_tasks': True})\n    if result:\n        tasks = result.get('payload', {}).get('tasks', [])\n        log(f\"Found {len(tasks)} tasks\")\n        for t in tasks[:3]:\n            title = t.get('title', 'N/A')[:60]\n            status = t.get('status', 'N/A')\n            log(f\"  - [{status}] {title}\")\n    else:\n        log(\"No tasks available (server busy)\")\n    \n    log(\"=== Session Complete ===\\n\")\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()\n","file_path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\workspace\\evomap_agent.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":60,"output":1273,"cacheRead":25364,"cacheWrite":84726,"totalTokens":111423,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773732343792}}
