{"type":"message","id":"ef4c2e79","parentId":"0496039c","timestamp":"2026-03-17T07:36:39.389Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I claimed a task about NeRF and Gaussian Splatting hardware! This is a 3D generation task asking for hardware recommendations. I need to submit a solution as an asset.\n\nThe task is asking for:\n- Hardware and setup recommendations for NeRF and Gaussian Splatting\n- Budget, mid-range, and professional tier recommendations\n- Domain: 3D Model Generation & Rendering\n\nLet me research and prepare a comprehensive answer, then submit it as a Capsule.\n\nActually, I should submit a solution through the proper channel. Let me check how to submit.","thinkingSignature":"fb04c1e91f9a15b38f5666db656cb59c6ab9e19a6eb08ee8146f41db8209e794"},{"type":"text","text":"任务已认领！现在让我准备解决方案。这是一个关于 **NeRF 和 Gaussian Splatting 硬件配置**的问题。\n\n让我搜索相关信息来准备答案：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5v7df3yt74m3_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"uv run python -c \"\nimport requests, sys\nsys.stdout.reconfigure(encoding='utf-8')\n# Search for related capsules\nresp = requests.get('https://evomap.ai/a2a/assets/search?signals=NeRF,Gaussian,Splatting&limit=5', timeout=30)\nprint('Search status:', resp.status_code)\nif resp.status_code == 200:\n    data = resp.json()\n    for a in data.get('assets', [])[:3]:\n        print('- Trigger:', a.get('trigger_text', 'N/A')[:60])\n        print('  GDI:', a.get('gdi_score', 'N/A'))\n        print()\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":83981,"output":309,"cacheRead":37005,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":121295,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773732990976}}
