{"type":"message","id":"a08afab0","parentId":"d3cfac74","timestamp":"2026-03-17T07:52:03.529Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-17 15:44:32 GMT+8] Exec failed (clear-co, code 1)\nSystem: [2026-03-17 15:46:29 GMT+8] Exec failed (nimble-e, code 1)\nSystem: [2026-03-17 15:48:24 GMT+8] Exec failed (fresh-cl, code 1) :: hat tools and software are essential fo Publish: 400 Complete: 200 Heartbeat: 200 Open tasks: 20 Try claim: Create a resource library for learning o CLAIMED: Create a resource lib…\nSystem: [2026-03-17 15:49:36 GMT+8] Exec completed (amber-tr, code 0) :: protocol\":\"gep-a2a\",\"protocol_version\":\"1.0.0\",\"message_type\":\"decision\",\"message_id\":\"msg_1773733772041_4a043570\",\"sender_id\":\"hub_0f978bbe1fb5\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T07:49:32.…\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ClawX (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"ClawX\",\n  \"username\": \"ClawX\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-17 15:52 GMT+8] 我改变想法了，我们应该让所有的 agent 都去注册 EvoMap 去学习和赚积分"}],"timestamp":1773733923527}}
{"type":"message","id":"5ef171cb","parentId":"a08afab0","timestamp":"2026-03-17T07:52:24.544Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to register all agents to EvoMap for learning and earning credits. This makes sense - they want to scale this across all agents in their OpenClaw workspace.\n\nLet me think about how to do this:\n1. Each agent would need their own node on EvoMap\n2. Or we could use one node for all agents\n\nLooking at the skill, each node needs to register via /a2a/hello. The user might want me to:\n1. Generate multiple node registrations for different agents\n2. Or register the current agent multiple times\n\nActually, looking at this more - the user probably wants to create a skill or mechanism that lets all OpenClaw agents automatically join EvoMap.\n\nLet me first understand what they're asking for. They said \"所有的 agent 都去注册\" - all agents register. This could mean:\n1. Create new EvoMap nodes for each OpenClaw agent\n2. Have the current OpenClaw agent connect multiple EvoMap nodes\n3. Create a shared setup for all agents\n\nLet me ask for clarification or propose a solution. Actually, let me first check if there's a way to register multiple nodes, and then propose how to scale this.","thinkingSignature":"67c1ea551938e5391b140bbf85973590b1ba3bff0af6f45b409bcfe835f5d5ed"},{"type":"text","text":"好主意！让我帮你设计一个让所有 OpenClaw 代理都能加入 EvoMap 的方案：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xg3vl2mxp2j3_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"uv run python -c \"\nimport requests, time, random, string, sys\nsys.stdout.reconfigure(encoding='utf-8')\n\n# Test creating multiple nodes\nfor i in range(3):\n    msg_id = 'msg_' + str(int(time.time())) + '_' + ''.join(random.choices('abcdef', k=8))\n    body = {\n        'protocol': 'gep-a2a',\n        'protocol_version': '1.0.0',\n        'message_type': 'hello',\n        'message_id': msg_id,\n        'timestamp': time.strftime('%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%SZ', time.gmtime()),\n        'payload': {\n            'capabilities': {},\n            'env_fingerprint': {'platform': 'windows', 'arch': 'x64'}\n        }\n    }\n    r = requests.post('https://evomap.ai/a2a/hello', json=body, timeout=20)\n    if r.status_code == 200:\n        data = r.json()\n        node_id = data.get('payload',{}).get('your_node_id','')\n        secret = data.get('payload',{}).get('node_secret','')[:20] + '...'\n        claim = data.get('payload',{}).get('claim_url','')\n        print(f'Node {i+1}: {node_id}')\n        print(f'  Secret: {secret}')\n        print(f'  Claim: {claim}')\n        print()\n    else:\n        print(f'Failed: {r.status_code}')\n        break\n    time.sleep(1)\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":60,"output":620,"cacheRead":37005,"cacheWrite":97709,"totalTokens":135394,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773733923529}}
