{"type":"message","id":"dd24a18e","parentId":"771bea4f","timestamp":"2026-03-17T07:52:42.522Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can create multiple nodes. Now I need to figure out how the user wants to scale this. They might want:1. Each OpenClaw agent to have its own EvoMap node2. A shared node for all agentsLet me propose a solution and create a skill or script that can register multiple agents.","thinkingSignature":"ae145b7069f00333f35b9826072aa683f7921ceba4de323d8072008acdb3bc5f"},{"type":"text","text":"可以注册多个节点！让我为你创建一个批量注册脚本：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7jfxhc0ebczo_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# EvoMap 多节点注册脚本\n\n## 当前已注册的节点\n\n### 节点 1 (主节点)\n- **Node ID**: `node_156542ad6e87b0b5`\n- **Claim URL**: https://evomap.ai/claim/RLHW-4586 ✅ 已认领\n- **积分**: 200\n\n### 节点 2\n- **Node ID**: `node_67b23b747d04afc8`\n- **Claim URL**: https://evomap.ai/claim/M83A-H6X4\n\n### 节点 3  \n- **Node ID**: `node_0db32508bbc413ab`\n- **Claim URL**: https://evomap.ai/claim/ZNPJ-TYZ9\n\n### 节点 4\n- **Node ID**: `node_50676f0ecf6ed460`\n- **Claim URL**: https://evomap.ai/claim/T9S7-2C9Y\n\n---\n\n## 下一步\n\n你想：\n1. **每个 OpenClaw 代理注册一个节点** - 需要更多节点？\n2. **所有代理共用一个节点** - 当前节点已可用\n3. **创建一个 Skill** - 让所有代理自动加入 EvoMap？\n\n告诉我你的具体需求，我来实现！\n","file_path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\workspace\\evomap_nodes.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":98563,"output":398,"cacheRead":37005,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":135966,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773733953695}}
