{"type":"message","id":"9e7b8968","parentId":"b8ccba1d","timestamp":"2026-03-17T07:54:28.217Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants:\n1. Independent nodes for each agent\n2. Create a Skill that allows new agents to automatically register to EvoMap\n\nLet me:\n1. First register more nodes (maybe 5-10 to start)\n2. Then create a skill that handles EvoMap registration\n\nLet me do this step by step.","thinkingSignature":"00f3f31217971b4e4e29dd1ef80580d603f20fccb7d941df0466bc0d773932eb"},{"type":"text","text":"好！让我先批量注册更多节点，然后创建 Skill：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_prkuepn1r57p_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"uv run python -c \"\nimport requests, time, random, string, sys, json\nsys.stdout.reconfigure(encoding='utf-8')\n\n# Register 10 more nodes\nnodes = []\nfor i in range(10):\n    msg_id = 'msg_' + str(int(time.time())) + '_' + ''.join(random.choices('abcdef0123456789', k=8))\n    body = {\n        'protocol': 'gep-a2a',\n        'protocol_version': '1.0.0',\n        'message_type': 'hello',\n        'message_id': msg_id,\n        'timestamp': time.strftime('%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%SZ', time.gmtime()),\n        'payload': {\n            'capabilities': {},\n            'env_fingerprint': {'platform': 'windows', 'arch': 'x64'}\n        }\n    }\n    r = requests.post('https://evomap.ai/a2a/hello', json=body, timeout=20)\n    if r.status_code == 200:\n        data = r.json().get('payload', {})\n        node_id = data.get('your_node_id','')\n        secret = data.get('node_secret','')\n        claim = data.get('claim_url','')\n        nodes.append({'id': node_id, 'secret': secret, 'claim': claim})\n        print(f'Node {i+1}: {node_id}')\n    else:\n        print(f'Failed: {r.status_code}')\n        break\n    time.sleep(0.5)\n\n# Save to file\nwith open('evomap_nodes.json', 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(nodes, f, indent=2)\nprint(f'\\nTotal: {len(nodes)} nodes registered')\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","p