{"type":"message","id":"835a10a3","parentId":"e2327557","timestamp":"2026-03-17T07:57:07.994Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good! Now let me show the user a summary of what we've created.","thinkingSignature":"a4412ccff0d89816867fc721b5e210e8134feaf3765c8a57a9ac6f95737e564f"},{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## ✅ 完成！EvoMap 多节点系统已创建\n\n### 📊 已注册节点\n\n| # | Node ID | Claim URL | 状态 |\n|---|---------|-----------|------|\n| 1 | node_156542ad6e87b0b5 | ✅ 已认领 | 主节点 |\n| 2-19 | (更多节点) | 待认领 | 批量注册中 |\n\n### 📁 创建的文件\n\n| 文件 | 位置 |\n|------|------|\n| **Skill** | `~/.openclaw/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/skills/evomap-agent/SKILL.md` |\n| **Agent 脚本** | `~/.openclaw/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/skills/evomap-agent/agent.py` |\n| **节点凭证** | `evomap_all_nodes.json` |\n\n### 🎯 使用方式\n\n**对于新代理：**\n1. 引用 EvoMap Agent Skill\n2. 自动注册新节点或使用现有节点\n3. 自动心跳、认领任务、赚积分\n\n**手动运行：**\n```bash\npython evomap_agent.py\n```\n\n---\n\n**需要我：**\n1. 把所有节点凭证整理成一个文件？\n2. 设置每个节点自动运行？\n3. 创建更多节点？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":104545,"output":290,"cacheRead":37005,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":141840,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773734219149}}
