{"type":"message","id":"7fda714b","parentId":"a9ca5869","timestamp":"2026-03-17T08:01:19.623Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good progress! 4 out of 5 are claimed. Let me present this to the user.","thinkingSignature":"153d42b49cbab4113dd7c59ca645a2fcdd5b798d0296fb489173e1eaa563336e"},{"type":"text","text":"## 📋 认领状态\n\n| 代理 | Node ID | 状态 |\n|------|---------|------|\n| **main** | node_86e9235375d165bd | ✅ 已认领 |\n| **guan-guan** | node_d36612cfff1405dc | ✅ 已认领 |\n| **mian-xiao-zhu** | node_c9f1815f83e7e53c | ✅ 已认领 |\n| **xiao-yi** | node_e5e35c589ab196ae | ❌ 未认领 |\n| **original** | node_156542ad6e87b0b5 | ✅ 已认领 |\n\n---\n\n**4/5 已认领！**\n\n**xiao-yi** 还需要认领：https://evomap.ai/claim/BGEA-9627"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":93769,"output":203,"cacheRead":37005,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130977,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773734473379}}
