{"type":"message","id":"415ef27d","parentId":"5bf3490e","timestamp":"2026-03-17T09:13:12.190Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting - the reputation breakdown shows different values. Let me explain:\n\n- **main**: 52.5 = 50 (base) + 2.5 (promotion)\n- **guan-guan**: 52.5 = 50 (base) + 2.5 (promotion)  \n- **mian-xiao-zhu**: 50 = 50 (base) + 0 (no promotion yet)\n- **xiao-yi**: 50 = 50 (base) + 0 (no promotion yet)\n\nThe base reputation is 50 for all claimed nodes. Then:\n- +2.5 for each promotion (promotion_rate * 25 weight * 0.1 maturity factor = 2.5)\n\nSo main and guan-guan have each 1 promotion, giving them +2.5 reputation.\n\nThe published count is different because:\n- Each agent independently submits solutions to tasks\n- Tasks get filled up (max 10 concurrent claimants)\n- Some agents submit more than others\n\nThe approval rate is:\n- main: 1/5 = 20%\n- guan-guan: 1/4 = 25%\n- mian-xiao-zhu: 0/1 = 0%\n- xiao-yi: 0/1 = 0%\n\nLet me explain this clearly to the user.","thinkingSignature":"e3e24ff837a5043d15f729007dfcbe723d3e9ed3bf19456b743e2d3a753435d5"},{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 声誉与发布差异分析\n\n### 各代理对比\n\n| 代理 | 声誉 | = | 基底 | + | 推广加分 | 发布 | 通过 | 拒绝 | 通过率 |\n|------|------|---|------|---|----------|------|------|------|--------|\n| **main** | 52.5 | = | 50 | + | 2.5 | 5 | 1 | 0 | 20% |\n| **guan-guan** | 52.5 | = | 50 | + | 2.5 | 4 | 1 | 0 | 25% |\n| **mian-xiao-zhu** | 50 | = | 50 | + | 0 | 1 | 0 | 0 | 0% |\n| **xiao-yi** | 50 | = | 50 | + | 0 | 1 | 0 | 0 | 0% |\n\n### 🔍 差异原因\n\n1. **声誉计算**：\n   - 基底：所有认领的节点都是 50\n   - 推广加分：每推广 1 个 = +2.5 声誉\n   - main 和 guan-guan 各有 1 个推广，所以 52.5\n\n2. **发布数量不同**：\n   - 每个代理独立竞争任务\n   - 任务有 10 个并发名额\n   - 先抢先得，有的代理抢到了，有的没抢到\n\n3. **通过率**：\n   - main: 1/5 = 20%\n   - guan-guan: 1/4 = 25%  \n   - mian-xiao-zhu: 0/1 = 0%\n   - xiao-yi: 0/1 = 0%\n\n需要我优化脚本让发布数量和通过率显示更清晰吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":121581,"out