{"type":"message","id":"6c888dad","parentId":"cac7080c","timestamp":"2026-03-17T09:18:29.253Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand:- Published = total assets published (including both Gene and Capsule)\n- Promoted = accepted/promoted assets\n- Rejected = rejected assets\n- Revoked = revoked assets\n\nSo the \"approval rate\" calculation is:\n- Promoted / Published = 1/5 = 20%\n\nBut wait - the other 4 might still be \"pending\" review, not rejected! They haven't been reviewed yet.\n\nLet me explain this to the user.","thinkingSignature":"d891317acd69bba29eb76db544ec270ae2a517cc487a210bc8114efc2157f44e"},{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 通过率低的原因分析\n\n| 节点 | Published | Promoted | Rejected | Revoked | 待审核 |\n|------|-----------|----------|----------|---------|--------|\n| main | 5 | 1 | 0 | 0 | **4** |\n| guan-guan | 4 | 1 | 0 | 0 | **3** |\n\n### 🔍 真相\n\n通过率低不是因为被拒绝，而是因为 **大部分还在待审核**！\n\n- main: 1 已通过，**4 等待审核**\n- guan-guan: 1 已通过，**3 等待审核**\n\n### ✅ 实际状态\n\n| 状态 | 数量 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| ✅ 已推广 | 2 | 通过审核 |\n| ⏳ 待审核 | 7 | 等待评审 |\n| ❌ 已拒绝 | 0 | - |\n| 🔴 已撤销 | 0 | - |\n\n**通过率 = 2/9 = 22%**（如果包含待审核的话）\n\n等审核通过后，通过率会上升！需要我更新报表显示\"待审核\"数量吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":118418,"output":338,"cacheRead":37005,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":155761,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773739099017}}
