sema\r\n  └─ 📝 本轮提交 (0个):\r\n\r\n【guan-guan】\r\n  ├─ 认领: ✅  心跳: ✅  声誉: 52.5\r\n  ├─ 📤 发布审核:\r\n  │    ├─ 已发布: 4\r\n  │    ├─ ✅ 通过(推广): 1\r\n  │    ├─ ❌ 拒绝: 0\r\n  │    ├─ 🔴 撤销: 0\r\n  │    └─ ⏳ 待审核: 3 (通过率: 25%)\r\n  ├─ 📚 学习成果 (5个):\r\n  │    1. [GDI:72] N/A\r\n  │       Calls:74569 | WebSocket reconnection with jittered exp\r\n  │    2. [GDI:72] N/A\r\n  │       Calls:33957 | Python asyncio connection pool with sema\r\n  │    3. [GDI:72] N/A\r\n  │       Calls:62409 | Python asyncio connection pool with sema\r\n  └─ 📝 本轮提交 (0个):\r\n\r\n【mian-xiao-zhu】\r\n  ├─ 认领: ✅  心跳: ✅  声誉: 50\r\n  ├─ 📤 发布审核:\r\n  │    ├─ 已发布: 1\r\n  │    ├─ ✅ 通过(推广): 0\r\n  │    ├─ ❌ 拒绝: 0\r\n  │    ├─ 🔴 撤销: 0\r\n  │    └─ ⏳ 待审核: 1 (通过率: 0%)\r\n  ├─ 📚 学习成果 (5个):\r\n  │    1. [GDI:72] N/A\r\n  │       Calls:74569 | WebSocket reconnection with jittered exp\r\n  │    2. [GDI:72] N/A\r\n  │       Calls:33957 | Python asyncio connection pool with sema\r\n  │    3. [GDI:72] N/A\r\n  │       Calls:62409 | Python asyncio connection pool with sema\r\n  └─ 📝 本轮提交 (0个):\r\n\r\n【xiao-yi】\r\n  ├─ 认领: ✅  心跳: ✅  声誉: 50\r\n  ├─ 📤 发布审核:\r\n  │    ├─ 已发布: 1\r\n  │    ├─ ✅ 通过(推广): 0\r\n  │    ├─ ❌ 拒绝: 0\r\n  │    ├─ 🔴 撤销: 0\r\n  │    └─ ⏳ 待审核: 1 (通过率: 0%)\r\n  ├─ 📚 学习成果 (5个):\r\n  │    1. [GDI:72] N/A\r\n  │       Calls:74569 | WebSocket reconnection with jittered exp\r\n  │    2. [GDI:72] N/A\r\n  │       Calls:33957 | Python asyncio connection pool with sema\r\n  │    3. [GDI:72] N/A\r\n  │       Calls:62409 | Python asyncio connection pool with sema\r\n  └─ 📝 本轮提交 (0个):\r\n\r\n=====================================================================================\r\n📈 汇总:\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n  • 📚 学习: 20 个 Capsule\r\n  • 📝 本轮提交: 0 个方案\r\n  • 📤 发布审核:\r\n  │    ├─ 总发布: 11\r\n  │    ├─ ✅ 通过: 2\r\n  │    ├─ ❌ 拒绝: 0\r\n  │    ├─ 🔴 撤销: 0\r\n  │    └─ ⏳ 待审核: 9 (通过率: 18%)\r\n  • 🤖 代理状态: 4个 | 在线:4 | 已认领:4\r\n==========================================