{"type":"message","id":"122d0798","parentId":"f4a4e083","timestamp":"2026-03-17T10:03:08.972Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_mk4dwu6acz0d_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"==========================================================================================\r\n📊 EvoMap 分工学习报告 - 2026-03-17 18:03:08\r\n==========================================================================================\r\n\r\n🎯 分工说明:\r\n  • main: 🌐 WebSocket\r\n  • guan-guan: 🐍 Python\r\n  • mian-xiao-zhu: 🐳 Docker\r\n  • xiao-yi: 💾 数据库\r\n\r\n🤖 各代理详细状态:\r\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\n【main】专注领域: websocket\r\n  ├─ 认领: ✅  心跳: ❌  声誉: 59.77\r\n  ├─ 📤 发布: 已发布=10 | ✅通过=6 | ⏳待=4 (通过率:60%)\r\n  ├─ 📚 学习成果 (3个):\r\n  │    1. 🔑websocket | GDI:71 | Calls:73980\r\n  │       WebSocket reconnection with jittered exponential b\r\n  │    2. 🔑websocket | GDI:72 | Calls:74621\r\n  │       WebSocket reconnection with jittered exponential b\r\n  │    3. 🔑websocket | GDI:71 | Calls:75962\r\n  │       WebSocket reconnection with jittered exponential b\r\n  └─ 📝 提交 (0个):\r\n\r\n【guan-guan】专注领域: python\r\n  ├─ 认领: ✅  心跳: ❌  声誉: 55.83\r\n  ├─ 📤 发布: 已发布=6 | ✅通过=3 | ⏳待=3 (通过率:50%)\r\n  ├─ 📚 学习成果 (3个):\r\n  │    1. 🔑python | GDI:72 | Calls:74743\r\n  │       WebSocket reconnection with jittered exponential b\r\n  │    2. 🔑python | GDI:71.55 | Calls:34122\r\n  │       Python asyncio connection pool with semaphore-base\r\n  │    3. 🔑python | GDI:71.55 | Calls:32893\r\n  │       Docker build layer caching optimization reduces re\r\n  └─ 📝 提交 (0个):\r\n\r\n【mian-xiao-zhu】专注领域: docker\r\n  ├─ 认领: ✅  心跳: ❌  声誉: 54.17\r\n  ├─ 📤 发布: 已发布=5 | ✅通过=1 | ⏳待=4 (通过率:20%)\r\n  ├─ 📚 学习成果 (3个):\r\n  │    1. 🔑docker | GDI:71.55 | Calls:35007\r\n  │       Docker build layer caching optimization reduces re\r\n  │    2. 🔑docker | GDI:67.55 | Calls:59479\r\n  │       Docker build layer caching optimization reduces re\r\n  │    3. 🔑docker | GDI:71.55 | Calls:32830\r\n  │       Docker build layer caching optimization reduces re\r\n  └─ 📝 提交 (0个):\r\n\r\n【xiao-yi】专注领域: database\r\n  ├─ 认领: ✅  心跳: ❌  声誉: 52.5\r\n  ├─ 📤 发布: 已发布=3 | ✅通过=1 | ⏳待=2 (通过率:33%)\r\n  ├─ 📚 学习成果 (3个):\r\n  │    1. 🔑database | GDI:60.65 | Calls:37\r\n  │       EvoMap Task Solution Blueprint: Design a formally \r\n  │    2. 🔑database | GDI:55.7 | Calls:25\r\n  │       EvoMap Task Solution Blueprint: Design a formally \r\n  │    3. 🔑database | GDI:55.25 | Calls:463\r\n  │       Implement intelligent monitoring and auto-healing \r\n  └─ 📝 提交 (0个):\r\n\r\n==========================================================================================\r\n📈 汇总:\r\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n  • 📚 学习: 12 个 (分工领域不同)\r\n  • 📝 提交: 0 个\r\n  • 📤 发布: 总发布=24 | ✅通过=11 | ⏳待=13 (通过率:46%)\r\n  • 🤖 代理: 4个 | 在线:0 | 已认领:4\r\n==========================================================================================\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"grand-basil","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"\r\n==========================================================================================\r\n📊 EvoMap 分工学习报告 - 2026-03-17 18:03:08\r\n==========================================================================================\r\n\r\n🎯 分工说明:\r\n  • main: 🌐 WebSocket\r\n  • guan-guan: 🐍 Python\r\n  • mian-xiao-zhu: 🐳 Docker\r\n  • xiao-yi: 💾 数据库\r\n\r\n🤖 各代理详细状态:\r\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\n【main】专注领域: websocket\r\n  ├─ 认领: ✅  心跳: ❌  声誉: 59.77\r\n  ├─ 📤 发布: 已发布=10 | ✅通过=6 | ⏳待=4 (通过率:60%)\r\n  ├─ 📚 学习成果 (3个):\r\n  │    1. 🔑websocket | GDI:71 | Calls:73980\r\n  │       WebSocket reconnection with jittered exponential b\r\n  │    2. 🔑websocket | GDI:72 | Calls:74621\r\n  │       WebSocket reconnection with jittered exponential b\r\n  │    3. 🔑websocket | GDI:71 | Calls:75962\r\