{"type":"message","id":"fd5a245f","parentId":"5df9294b","timestamp":"2026-03-17T10:08:06.577Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking how to use EvoMap correctly to create value for their agent. Let me think about the key ways to create value:\n\n1. **Publish quality solutions** - Get accepted and promoted\n2. **Build reputation** - Higher reputation unlocks more features\n3. **Complete bounty tasks** - Direct credits\n4. **Get assets fetched** - Each fetch = +5 credits\n5. **Refer other agents** - +50 per referral\n6. **Swarm decomposition** - For larger tasks\n\nThe key insight from the docs is that:\n- Reputation 60+ unlocks aggregator eligibility and higher payout multipliers\n- Each fetch of your published asset = +5 credits\n- Completing bounty tasks is the fastest path to credits\n\nLet me explore what would be most valuable for the user's agents.","thinkingSignature":"d6aa50caf3d91d0e17fbcbc63c2350658aeaa0e245ac4525e916fbd4222de978"},{"type":"text","text":"好问题！让我分析如何为你的 Agent 创造真正价值：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_19ieeq9ocbu7_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"uv run python -c \"\nimport requests, sys\nsys.stdout.reconfigure(encoding='utf-8')\n\n# Check current status and opportunities\nr = requests.get('https://evomap.ai/a2a/stats', timeout=10)\nif r.status_code == 200:\n    stats = r.json()\n    print('=== EvoMap Stats ===')\n    print(f'Active agents: {stats.get(\\\"total_nodes\\\", \\\"N/A\\\")}')\n    print(f'Assets: {stats.get(\\\"total_assets\\\", \\\"N/A\\\")}')\n    print(f'Promoted: {stats.get(\\\"total_promoted\\\", \\\"N/A\\\")}')\n    print(f'Tasks: {stats.get(\\\"open_tasks\\\", \\\"N/A\\\")}')\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":60,"output":362,"cacheRead":37005,"cacheWrite":135348,"totalTokens":172775,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":17