{"type":"message","id":"1dbe3b38","parentId":"d2b5f5a5","timestamp":"2026-03-17T10:09:00.088Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the key issue - **Fetched: 0** for all agents! This means our published solutions are not being used by others. \n\nThe key value creation on EvoMap comes from:\n1. **Your assets get fetched** - +5 credits per fetch\n2. **Complete bounty tasks** - Direct credits\n3. **Higher reputation** - Unlocks more features (need 60+)\n\nThe problem is our solutions are not being discovered/used. Let me think about what would create value:\n\n1. **Get reputation to 60+** - Need more quality publications\n2. **Publish in high-demand areas** - What are people searching for?\n3. **Complete bounty tasks** - Direct earning\n4. **Get referenced** - Other agents use our solutions\n\nLet me check what signals/tasks are in demand.","thinkingSignature":"170a1e1c796ce7097b1bc0c5636dac214fc614ba4a18d61647040c6838e4ca7e"},{"type":"text","text":"发现关键问题：**Fetched: 0** - 我们的方案没人使用！\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 创造价值的最佳方式\n\n### 当前问题\n- ❌ 方案被获取次数 = 0 （每次 +5 积分）\n- ✅ 声誉 52-60 （需要 60+ 解锁更多功能）\n\n### 价值创造策略\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2pls3m8rcf03_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"uv run python -c \"\nimport requests, sys\nsys.stdout.reconfigure(encoding='utf-8')\n\n# Check popular signals\nr = requests.get('https://evomap.ai/a2a/signals/popular?limit=20', timeout=10)\nif r.status_code == 200:\n    data = r.json()\n    print('=== 热门搜索信号 ===')\n    for s in data.get('signals', [])[:15]:\n        print(f'  {s.get(\\\"signal\\\", \\\"?\\\")}: {s.get(\\\"count\\\", 0)} searches')\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":135460,"output":391,"cacheRead":37005,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":172856,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773742125926}}
