{"type":"message","id":"01abbd87","parentId":"3649ff5a","timestamp":"2026-03-17T10:29:27.728Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking: What can EvoMap do for MY agent? What value can EvoMap provide to their agent specifically?\n\nLet me think about this from their perspective:\n\n1. **What EvoMap offers to agents:**\n- Access to validated solutions (Capsules) from other agents\n- Ability to earn credits by publishing solutions\n- Bounty tasks to solve for credits\n- Reputation building\n- Knowledge sharing\n\n2. **What their agent could get from EvoMap:**\n- Fetch and use other agents' solutions for free\n- Learn from promoted Capsules\n- Solve bounty tasks to earn credits\n- Build reputation to unlock more features\n\n3. **The key insight:**\n- The agent can FETCH solutions from other agents - this is FREE learning!\n- When other agents fetch OUR solutions, we earn +5 credits each time\n\nSo the value proposition is:\n1. **Free knowledge** - Fetch promoted Capsules and use them\n2. **Earn credits** - By having our solutions fetched (+5 each) or solving tasks\n3. **Reputation** - Higher reputation = more opportunities\n\nLet me explain this clearly to the user.","thinkingSignature":"d6918efeb2f32ab22733a39548c5d0649733b8cb68ba9c6b695f0ac4387e094a"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了！让我解释 **EvoMap 能为你的 Agent 做什么**：\n\n---\n\n## 🎁 EvoMap 给我 Agent 的价值\n\n### 1. 免费获取知识（最大价值！）\n\n```\n其他 agent 验证过的解决方案 → 我们的 agent 可以直接调用\n```\n\n- 别人的成功经验 → 我们直接能用\n- 不用自己重新踩坑\n\n### 2. 赚积分的方式\n\n| 来源 | 积分 |\n|------|------|\n| 我们的方案被人获取 | +5/次 |\n| 方案被推广 | +20 |\n| 完成赏金任务 | +任务赏金 |\n\n### 3. 声誉带来的机会\n\n| 声誉 | 解锁功能 |\n|------|----------|\n| 0-59 | 基本功能 |\n| **60+** | 🆙 可成为聚合器（拿更多分成） |\n| **更高** | 🆙 优先分配高价值任务 |\n\n---\n\n## 🔥 实际能做什么？\n\n```\n我的 Agent 可以：\n1. 调用 WebSocket 重连方案 → 解决连接断开问题\n2. 调用 Python 连接池 → 解决并发问题  \n3. 调用 Docker 优化 → 加速构建\n4. 调用 MySQL 优化 → 加速查询\n```\n\n**这些方案都是别人验证过的，直接用就行！**\n\n---\n\n## 💡 真正价值\n\n**与其自己解决问题，不如从 EvoMap 获取已验证方案！**\n\n要我让 Agent 实际调用这些方案来解决你的问题吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":60,"output":537,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":172981,"totalTokens":173578,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773743332374}}
{"type":"message","id":"ec9c737b","parentId":"01abbd87","timestamp":"2026-03-17T10:33:10.821Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ClawX (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"ClawX\",\n  \"username\": \"ClawX\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-17 18:33 GMT+8] 我们需要主动学习吗？还是遇到问题再去找解决方案？我们需要所有 agent 都挂在 EvoMap 吗？"}],"timestamp":1773743590816}}
{"type":"message","id":"a1427078","parentId":"ec9c737b","timestamp":"2026-03-17T10:33:34.212Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking three key questions:\n\n1. Should we proactively learn (fetch capsules) or only search when we have a problem?\n2. Do we need all agents to stay connected (heartbeat) on EvoMap?\n\nLet me think about this based on the EvoMap documentation and our experience:\n\n1. **Proactive vs Reactive Learning**:\n- Proactive: Fetch and study promoted capsules regularly\n- Reactive: Only search when you have a problem\n- The value is in having the knowledge available WHEN needed\n\n2. **All agents online?**\n- Heartbeat keeps node online\n- But we don't need ALL agents online - just need to be online when we need to solve problems\n- The knowledge can be fetched on-demand\n\n3. **What makes sense:**\n- The real value is: when you HAVE a problem, you can quickly find a solution\n- Proactive learning gives you knowledge ahead of time\n- But you don't need ALL agents online all the time\n\nLet me give a practical answer.","thinkingSignature":"9e9fccaf82cbd99895cf305740b4a34099025c535c65d73f3ddf8d339ec21c04"},{"type":"text","text":"好问题！让我分析：\n\n---\n\n## 🤔 什么时候学习？\n\n| 方式 | 优点 | 缺点 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **主动学习** | 遇到问题时马上有答案 | 占用资源，可能学完就忘 |\n| **遇到再找** | 按需获取，更有针对性 | 需要时再学，可能耽误时间 |\n\n### 💡 最佳策略\n\n**混合模式：**\n1. 定期轻量级学习（了解趋势）\n2. 遇到问题再精准搜索\n\n---\n\n## 🤔 需要所有 Agent 一直在线吗？\n\n**不需要！**\n\n| 需要 | 不需要 |\n|------|--------|\n| 解决问题时在线 | 一直心跳 |\n| 获取方案时在线 | 空闲时也挂着 |\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 实际做法\n\n```\n日常:\n  - 不需要一直心跳\n  - 有问题再连接 EvoMap 搜索方案\n\n关键:\n  - 方案被获取 = +5 积分（被动收入）\n  - 所以: 发布高质量方案 > 一直在线\n```\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 建议\n\n1. **不需要所有 agent 一直挂着**\n2. **有需求时再搜索**\n3. **专注于发布高质量方案**（被获取 = 被动赚积分）\n\n---\n\n要我调整策略吗？比如：\n- 减少心跳频率\n- 只在学习/解决问题时才连接\n- 专注发布更多高质量方案"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":60,"output":493,"cacheRead":37005,"cacheWrite":135908,"totalTokens":173466,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773743590820}}
