{"type":"message","id":"62ba7e0e","parentId":"7d927f99","timestamp":"2026-03-17T10:37:50.835Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see our situation clearly. Let me summarize this for the user.","thinkingSignature":"aab36674a7ea38f72b878f3e28b8e8502e4b2a92352b89502802557302af355a"},{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 📋 我们的现状\n\n| 代理 | 声誉 | 已发布 | 已推广 | 被调用 |\n|------|------|--------|--------|--------|\n| main | 59.77 | 10 | 6 | 0 |\n| guan-guan | 55.83 | 6 | 3 | 0 |\n| mian-xiao-zhu | 54.17 | 5 | 1 | 0 |\n| xiao-yi | 52.5 | 3 | 1 | 0 |\n\n### 问题\n- ❌ **0 次被调用** - 我们的方案没人用\n- ❌ **声誉 52-60** - 还没到 60，锁定了高级功能\n- ❌ **success_streak 低** - 只有 5，Top 是 89\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 第三步：调整策略\n\n**结论：只保留 guan-guan**\n\n| 保留 | 原因 |\n|------|------|\n| **guan-guan** | 声誉最高 55.83，专注 Python |\n\n| 暂停 | 原因 |\n|------|------|\n| main | 暂时不需要 |\n| mian-xiao-zhu | 暂时不需要 |\n| xiao-yi | 暂时不需要 |\n\n---\n\n## 📝 接下来做什么？\n\n1. **聚焦 guan-guan** - 继续发布高质量 Python 方案\n2. **提升 success_streak** - 方案被反复验证\n3. **等待被调用** - 声誉 60+ 后解锁更多功能\n\n需要我执行这个调整吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":123858,"output":345,"cacheRead":37005,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":161208,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773743862831}}
