{"type":"message","id":"1d9c6a58","parentId":"2b8a3745","timestamp":"2026-03-17T10:41:15.373Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to:\n1. Focus only on guan-guan, remove other nodes\n2. guan-guan should not focus on specific domain\n3. Evaluate what content we have that can be turned into high-quality solutions\n4. How to improve success_streak\n\nLet me analyze what we have and what makes a high success_streak.\n\nFirst, let's understand what success_streak means - it's the number of times a solution has been successfully used/verified.\n\nThe key insight from the top capsule:\n- success_streak: 89 (very high)\n- confidence: 0.99\n- call_count: 74,929\n\nsuccess_streak goes up when:\n- The solution is actually used to solve problems\n- Each successful use increases the streak\n\nSo to increase success_streak, we need:\n1. Publish solutions that people actually want to use\n2. Have the solution be relevant to common problems\n\nFor guan-guan (no specific domain), we should look at:\n- What problems are commonly searched for\n- What solutions have high demand\n\nLet me search for popular signals and understand what we can offer.","thinkingSignature":"4072cb0bfba7a727d5e4a2200ff084f7e91c4b45b6eda146023576699270c97d"},{"type":"text","text":"好！让我分析 guan-guan 的策略：\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 Guan-guan 现状分析\n\n首先，让我看看热门问题和我们可以提供的内容：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3it8rpj8lrb2_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"uv run python -c \"\nimport requests\n# Get popular signals\nr = requests.get('https://evomap.ai/a2a/signals/popular?limit=30', timeout=15)\nif r.status_code == 200:\n    signals = r.json().get('signals', [])\n    print('=== 热门信号 (需求) ===')\n    for s in signals[:20]:\n        print(s.get('signal', '?'), ':', s.get('count', 0))\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":60,"output":386,"cacheRead":37005,"cacheWrite":124038,"totalTokens":161489,"cost":