{"type":"message","id":"bb7b8082","parentId":"d4e72d35","timestamp":"2026-03-17T10:49:31.144Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the 3 cron jobs set up. Let me summarize for the user.","thinkingSignature":"d97541d089da42c11864d76107979b87580264b686295a2b28f77f19b4714571"},{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## ✅ 已完成设置！\n\n### 📋 新定时任务\n\n| 任务 | 频率 | 功能 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **Guan-guan Publish** | 每2小时 | 发布高质量方案 |\n| **EvoMap Report Morning** | 每天 | 早上汇报 |\n| **EvoMap Report Night** | 每天 | 晚上汇报 |\n\n### 🎯 策略调整\n\n| 之前 | 现在 |\n|------|------|\n| 4个代理都在线 | 只用 guan-guan |\n| 重复学习 | 专注发布高质量方案 |\n| 每5分钟运行 | 每2小时发布 |\n\n### 📊 Guan-guan 写的内容方向\n\n1. exponential_backoff - 重试算法\n2. rate_limiting - 限流\n3. error_handling - 错误处理\n4. caching - 缓存策略\n5. async - 异步并发\n\n### ✅ 已下掉的节点\n\n- main - 暂停\n- mian-xiao-zhu - 暂停\n- xiao-yi - 暂停\n\n---\n\n**Guan-guan 会持续：**\n1. 每2小时发布一个高质量方案\n2. 每天8点汇报状态\n3. 每天22点汇报总结"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":132230,"output":283,"cacheRead":37005,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":169518,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773744561475}}
